description:
The Alex Jones Show

Tuesday January 20, 2009.

Alex will have total coverage of the Obama inauguration going into over drive. Guests include Ron Paul, Luke Rudkowski of WeAreChange, who will be live in Washington covering the events. Alex will appear on Russia Today during the show and Mike Rivero will sit in via webcam. 

Hour-1: Luke Rudkowski then Ron Paul then Mike Rivero takes over as host.

Hour-2: Mike Rivero as host - News - then Alex comes back as host with Mike Rivero as guest.

Hour-3: Mike Rivero as guest then news and open lines.

Hour-4: News and open lines.

Hour-5: News and open lines then Alex on Russia Today.oday.
